阿黛尔感谢粉丝在慕尼黑驻场期间的“非凡体验”：“我真的很感动” https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-thanks-fans-for-phenomenal-experience-on-munich-residency-i-am-truly-touched-3790352?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=adele-感谢粉丝们在慕尼黑驻地期间的非凡体验，我真的很感动Tom SkinnerWed, 04 Sep 2024 07:17:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3790352 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿黛尔在德国慕尼黑舞台现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手即将从音乐界休息很长时间</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-thanks-fans-for-phenomenal-experience-on-munich-residency-i-am-truly-touched-3790352">阿黛尔感谢粉丝在慕尼黑驻场的“非凡体验”：“我真的很感动”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿黛尔在德国慕尼黑舞台现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Adelethanks-fans-Munich-residency-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>回顾了她最近在慕尼黑的驻场演出，并在一篇感人的帖子中感谢粉丝们带来的“非凡体验”。</p><p>上个月，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/adele-30-album-review-dependable-pop-titan-finally-mixes-things-up-3096613">“30”</a>歌手在德国<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-prepares-to-kick-off-bloody-exciting-munich-residency-heres-everything-you-need-to-know-3780527">专门建造的可容纳 80,000 人的 Messe München 体育馆进行了 10 场演出</a>，这是她自 2016 年以来首次在欧洲大陆演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/adele-30-album-review-dependable-pop-titan-finally-mixes-things-up-3096613">阿黛尔 – “30”专辑评论：可靠的流行巨星终于把事情搞混了</a></strong></li></ul><p>此后，她宣布在 10 月和 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-announces-rescheduled-las-vegas-residency-dates-following-illness-3612322">重新安排拉斯维加斯驻场音乐会</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-announces-break-from-performing-i-will-not-see-you-for-an-incredibly-long-time-3789536">，她将暂停演出一段时间</a>。 “在那之后，我将在很长一段时间内见不到你，”她在慕尼黑的最后一场演出中说道。</p><p>今年夏天早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-i-dont-have-any-plans-for-new-music-at-all-3775417">阿黛尔证实她“根本没有任何新音乐计划”</a> ，并表示她想在即将到来的休息期间追求“其他创造性的事情”。</p><p>昨天（9 月 3 日），这位明星在社交媒体上发帖，公开了她在慕尼黑的庞大驻地。她还分享了一段专业拍摄的视频，其中包含现场约会的片段。</p><p> “哇！哇！哇！慕尼黑你太棒了！多么奇妙的经历啊。阿黛尔在标题中写道：“我真的被每场演出中每个人所流露出的真诚的爱和善意所感动。”</p><p> “这是最好的氛围。我从来没有见过像这样的演出，它真的很壮观，我非常荣幸能被邀请参加这些演出。我希望那些来过的人在“阿黛尔世界”度过了最美好的时光。我度过了一生中最愉快的时光，为它添加了所有个人和身临其境的感觉。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_c7ay3imQB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; borde